query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('assert',
'aurelia',
'boto3',
'derby',
'html-helper',
'python-2.x',
'sql-server-2016')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow') group by t1.name;
